'''Fhnark & Company Exotic Foodstuffs''' was an exotic [[Foodstuff/Legends|food]] and delicacies supplier founded by [[Fhnark]]. They were noted suppliers of fine [[nala tree frog]]s. [[Borga Besadii Diori|Borga]] the [[Hutt/Legends|Hutt]] was a large customer.<ref name="The New Jedi Order: Agents of Chaos II: Jedi Eclipse">''[[The New Jedi Order: Agents of Chaos II: Jedi Eclipse]]''</ref>

[[Jabba Desilijic Tiure/Legends|Jabba]] the Hutt also ordered his favorite [[trufflite]]s from them. Their motto was, ''"We cater to the galaxy degenerates' appetites."''<ref name="The Mandalorian Armor">''[[The Mandalorian Armor]]''</ref>

